snippet.title: Rebel Cops - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
No warrant required - Rebel Cops is OUT NOW!

The This Is the Police tactical spin-off is available for just $9.99 / €9.99 on PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch, offering 15 hours of challenging gameplay.

Get it on Steam: http://n.thq.com/KHud30pxZQU
Buy it on PlayStation 4 - US: http://n.thq.com/DneN30pxZRr
But it on PlayStation 4 - EU: http://n.thq.com/5rEp30pxZRl
Grab it on Xbox One: http://n.thq.com/9xLa30pxZR6
Snag a Nintendo Switch version: coming soon
